<div style="position:absolute;left:225.05px;top:231.02px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">INTRODUCTION</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:56.64px;top:278.69px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">A very warm welcome to our one of a kind Dog Care Course! We have</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:56.64px;top:295.73px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">structured this course in a way that it consists of photos and text on</span></div>
